\cs19\fs22\super\insrsid16142371 \chftn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs22\insrsid16142371  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs22\lang9226\langfe3082\langnp9226\insrsid16142371 En sentencia C-1232 de 2005, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PersonName}
